description: The stone stele that conceals most of one wall is itself partially hidden behind the cover of a paneled screen.  A domed glaes case sits near a wooden arch, while a low table is overshadowed by a carved pillar and wooden statue.  The polished plank floor and high silver gilt-paneled ceiling reflect the multicolored daylight coming in through an arched mosaic of glaesine tiles, which wraps around the silvered rectangle of a slender door.
